data.description: Updated, move in ready 3 bed, 1 bath home in Falcon Heights gated community. Some recent updates include; new flooring throughout, enlarged bathroom with new wall tiles, lighting fixtures, back porch and work room/storage area. Nice sized fully fenced back yard with storage shed and alley access. This community offers a neighborhood park, RV/Boat Storage and gated security that locks at dusk. HOA covers water, sewer, garbage, snow removal, front yard maintenance, exterior paint and roof maintenance. Subject to Seller finding suitable housing.
